1
00:00:00,009 --> 00:00:01,975
<i>Sebelumnya di The Last
Man on Earth...</i>

2
00:00:01,976 --> 00:00:04,438
Kami rasa kau harus repopulasi
dengan Melissa.

3
00:00:04,463 --> 00:00:05,561
